<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/Steam_title_lovelycharacters_EN.png?t=1737280566\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're not on your own on this journey. Plenty of playful friends will help you along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/Trailer_AsfaliaFear_Mix_EN_2024-10-23.gif?t=1737280566\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/Steam_title_stickers_EN.png?t=1737280566\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A collection of beautifully illustrated stickers awaits you. Can you find them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/stickers.gif?t=1737280566\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/Steam_title_minigames_EN.png?t=1737280566\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fun to the power of fun. Wait... I wonder if there's a fishing game too?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/shmup.gif?t=1737280566\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/Steam_title_cheese_EN.png?t=1737280566\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Because it tastes grate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/cheese.gif?t=1737280566\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gotcha!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2436410/33a44b272123253963548ef